notes.text: Previously Ground Cover 'crystal' was not properly counted for Crystal Match Counts. This has now been fixed resulting in some ranking changes when Thematic Matches is turned on. We are very sorry for the original inaccuracy.

notes.title: rarity.tools B Rankings optional version, doesn't double count score for Space backgrounds.
notes.text: Because all Space backgrounds are either Ancient Realm or Elder Realm pots, community members suggested that they were being given too much score. In B rankings 'Background Pot Combined' score is used instead of 'Pot' to fix this, however the B rankings did not get enough support from the community. Currently leaving A rankings as default but B rankings are also available as an option.

notes.title: Experimental Trait Counts!
notes.text:
A ranking with 'Trait Counts' is also included. A trait is counted for
- Head is not Bald
- Clothes is not Naked
- Eyes is not NoEyes
- Mouth is not Plain or NoAccessory.
Trait Counts weight is set as 0.1 as this is enough for 3 traits to be the top ones while 4 traits don't get boosted too much (as they don't look very unique). Please note that while the rankings are still new they might be subject to changes!
